import React, { Fragment } from 'react';
import { BoardRow, Status } from './style';

import Square from '../Square';

const Board = ({ status }) => (
  <Fragment>
    <Status>{status}</Status>
    <BoardRow>
      <Square>1</Square>
      <Square>2</Square>
      <Square>3</Square>
    </BoardRow>
    <BoardRow>
      <Square>4</Square>
      <Square>5</Square>
      <Square>6</Square>
    </BoardRow>
    <BoardRow>
      <Square>7</Square>
      <Square>8</Square>
      <Square>9</Square>
    </BoardRow>
  </Fragment>
);

export default Board;
